The paper discusses research and development in unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), which involves robotics, artificial intelligence, computer vision, control systems, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics and Control), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
